{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then in 1932, when I was about three years old, we moved out of that house for two reasons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Number one, the Germans had built a new bridge over the Rhine, and the access dam for the railroad came right in front of the house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as a result, you couldn't see anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a very high dam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the other reason was that my mother's youngest sister had just married and was moving away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my grandparents felt that they didn't want to live alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the three of us moved in with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And mother did most of the cooking, although my grandmother supervised everything and was an excellent cook also.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They sort of managed the house together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And where we lived there was in a house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "On the first floor was the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then the top two floors were living quarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So my grandfather, my father were very close to the business at all times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather's name was Elias Kling and my grandmother was Mina Kling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather was a very easygoing man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember him best as going to work in the morning, coming home for lunch, and then wanting his nap.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody could breathe while he was taking his nap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then, after his nap, he would go back to work-- came up at 4:00 and would expect a cup of coffee and a fresh roll on his plate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmother was a very religious person, more so than my father-- my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was totally Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when she couldn't go to services, she would pray at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She prayed mornings and evening in the living room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when she prayed, we had to tippy-toe around the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
